help.title: Help
help.description:
**Leveling system**
- Mindgame tracks your voice and activity on the Discord server and awards experience points for your activity.
- You will advance as you earn more experience points.
- Each level unlocks new level permissions such as access to exclusive channels or roles.

**Commands**
- `/ranking` Shows your ranking on the server.
- `/commits` Sends the latest source code commits.
- `/color` Allows configuring a custom role.
- `/help` Sends help (u looking at).
- `/ephemeral-channel` Set up ephemeral channel (messages in this channel will be deleted after time).

**Context menus**
- `Follow` Receive a notification every time the followed user comes back from an ≥8 hour break.
- `Show user profile` Shows the user profile.
- `Unfollow` Stop receiving notifications.
help.footer: Use quick buttons to navigate even faster.
